en_164907_0	One person died and two others sustained injuries following a gem mine collapse in Madara area in Nivithigala – Ratnapura.
en_164907_1	The deceased is a 34 year old resident of Madara – Nivithigala.
en_164907_2	The two injured were admitted to Ratnapura hospital and a spokesperson at the hospital stated that their condition is not critical.
en_164907_3	It is reported that the mine was operating illegally in a privately owned property.
